614
00:59:52,714 --> 00:59:56,301
BOOKSTORE JOURNAL
A GOODNIGHT BOOKSTORE PRIVATE BLOG POST

615
00:59:56,384 --> 00:59:57,594
POSTED BY SEOP

616
00:59:57,677 --> 01:00:02,265
There is only one good thing about winter.

617
01:00:02,807 --> 01:00:05,310
It's when the leaves
that were blocking my window fall

618
01:00:05,393 --> 01:00:08,021
and I can see your window
across from mine.

619
01:00:08,104 --> 01:00:12,692
When Christmas comes
and New Year's Day approaches,

620
01:00:13,484 --> 01:00:19,866
you return to this village for a few days.

621
01:00:24,037 --> 01:00:27,415
I hope you're not upset
about what I said to the group.

622
01:00:27,498 --> 01:00:31,085
It's all in the past anyway. Right?

623
01:00:31,169 --> 01:00:33,463
-Move!
-What are you doing tonight?

624
01:00:34,047 --> 01:00:36,382
I know a fun place.
Do you want to go with me?

625
01:00:36,466 --> 01:00:37,383
It changed.

626
01:00:37,467 --> 01:00:39,385
Willow leaves, right? It's pretty.

627
01:00:40,303 --> 01:00:42,347
-Where are you going so early?
-To my part-time job.

628
01:00:42,930 --> 01:00:45,475
There's not much to do.
I rarely get customers.

629
01:00:45,558 --> 01:00:47,935
I just need to watch the place, right?

630
01:00:48,019 --> 01:00:49,729
I'm so glad you're here.

631
